name: Portal Pups
description:
This is a special for the community OBJKT 4 OBJKT event on Twitter.

Jax is a feisty 2kg Pomeranian who likes to sink his teeth into anything and everything.

- Likes: cuddles, naps, bullying Loki, swimming, staring into space
- Dislikes: loud noises, scary humans, not being able to reach his toys

Loki is an emotionally unstable gen-Z dog who identifies as a wolf.

- Likes: long walks, chasing stuff, ribs, crypto investing, squeaky toys
- Dislikes: squirrels, the neighbours dog, the groomer, waiting for food
